data.description: Back on the market.  Motivated seller.  Built in 1906 this charming 1270 sqft home in Riverdale features 3 bathrooms, 1 bath, 1 car detached garage, a decent-sized yard with an apple tree.  There's a 300-ft walkable crawl space for all your storage needs.  Bring your creative imagination/ideas and make this your next home.  Submit reasonable offers for seller to consider.
